thread.title: Diane E Hazelet
thread.title_full: Premium Mortgage reviewed by Diane E Hazelet

author: Diane E Hazelet
title: Diane E Hazelet
text: I have worked with Premium for quite a few years now. First and foremost because PAUL WINTERHALTER is there. I have been licensed for 28+ years and have always had a great experience working with him. His knowledge surpasses any other loan officer that I have worked with, I would trust him with all of my clients. If there is ever an issue that Paul cannot handle (office issues) then Darlene Williams is there to take charge and that she does! I have always had a great working relationship with Darlene Woodworth and Theresa Pera too. Kudo's to Premium for keeping my clients happy and getting them in to their new homes!
